{"tid":820851,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食評]—順豐排骨麵","createTime":"2018-09-15T16:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T16:57:59.000Z","uid":182683,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b693ebe32220e6eb6c199781dc7257e85464ad3","tid":820851,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"地點：順豐排骨麵 天后<br />\n<br />\n依間野開左幾廿年地圖都仲係搵唔到名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，喺個暗角到平時行過都唔會見到，但次次黎到都幾多人食。<br />\n睇個名就個排骨係主打，我試過幾次都唔錯，但係我覺得醉雞同燻魚整得都好正！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我永遠唔會叫菜飯，因為冇咩味，麵就算冇餸都可以單獨食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/235606_434cb8842f4f47ebd16bf535b8f8c381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F235606_434cb8842f4f47ebd16bf535b8f8c381.png&h=8bf7748e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/235607_96c1160f351f487417072e888bc281ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F235607_96c1160f351f487417072e888bc281ab.png&h=d739c9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燻魚擔擔麵$60 <br />\n味道：<br />\n講講個麵先，普通陽春麵黎冇咩特別，個湯先係重點，我覺得擔擔麵個湯一定要杰同重麻醬同花生味，再加少少花椒油同辣就完美。<br />\n今次有少少失望，個湯稀左味唔夠，同埋冇左面個堆炒肉碎，仲要個辣唔香得個辣味，失敗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n到個燻魚，未食過嘅人可能食唔慣，個味係偏甜，燻魚其實個魚係唔會煙燻過嘅，係炸完有個甜嘅汁痴左係上面，同埋可以凍食，所以個質地唔似魚肉，但連埋個汁食好香口食到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，依到個魚整得幾好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n價錢：<br />\n麵同魚份量都正常，飽就一定飽，但$60個麵應該要有番以前個水準，依加咁就差左少少！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n最後想講講杯豆漿，其實好多地方都係咁，跟餐豆漿係就係免費，但可唔可以唔好完全冇豆味，同飲水冇分別！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n評分：6/10<br />\n評語：擔擔麵唔夠麻醬，失敗！<br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost&d=Z9Zr0DXAtFvpXCOZckdzrv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2a2fcba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube(整野食):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw%2Ffeatured&d=Z9Zr0DXAtFvpXCOZckdzrv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9c75ee4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0783fe55750ac48925815b9576ec26daaf9d049d","tid":820851,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"燻魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d188089dfdf0a2a8f873b821f76f2dac7a8396","tid":820851,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624eb803847caa119e8ff37fff1936f65d64afc2","tid":820851,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0783fe55750ac48925815b9576ec26daaf9d049d","tid":820851,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"燻魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ebcb1dab7c01372eca5a6dcc4721e78869cfb5","tid":820851,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{